The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 07 August 2011


[sebaygo1]


The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.

The Infowars web site describes today's broadcast as follows.

On this Sunday Edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks about the downing of a helicopter in Afghanistan, killing members of SEAL Team 6 that allegedly killed Osama bin Laden, and the cover-up of that operation. Alex also talks about the faltering economy and other important news.
